Name: Fight desserts
About the game: Play from a bird's eye view. Take a house as the main battle scene. Control a single character to face endless born enemies from all around. And your enemies are as big as you ..... cake?! Shoot around with mouse control. No saved! Each game is a brand new start. So....Getting achievements is a bit difficult.
